thread.title: Cody Maya and Meg
thread.title_full: SelfStorage.com reviewed by Cody Maya and Meg

author: Cody Maya and Meg
title: Cody Maya and Meg
text:
We originally set up to utilize their location for a UHAUL rental, but UHAUL website and their staff were less then helpful and confused our reservation with another location entirely...
Carla at the front desk was amazing and helped us locate the services we needed and we came back the next day to rent a unit from her.
I will recommend this location every time.
